Why This Matters
Prompt injection is listed in the OWASP Top 10 for LLM Applications as the #1 vulnerability in AI systems.
As organisations deploy AI tools internally — AI assistants, automated analysts, chatbots with access to internal data — prompt injection becomes an attack surface that traditional security tools don't cover.
This tool demonstrates understanding of that gap and a practical approach to closing it.
